15 (d) Such security for repayment shall be specified and shall be upon such terms
16 and conditions as the corporation deems reasonably necessary or practicable
17 to ensure[insure] all repayments.
18 (7) No funds from the housing development fund shall be used to carry on propaganda
19 or otherwise attempt to influence legislation.
20 (8) (a) Notwithstanding other provisions of this section, the corporation may make
21 loans secured by a mortgage from the housing development fund to enable a
22 person[ sixty-two (62) years of age or older] who owns the home in which he
